    "id": "v20"
  }, "v20"), mdx("p", null, "cho n\xEAn CH\xDAA g\u1EA1t b\u1ECF to\xE0n d\xE2n \xCDt-ra-en. Ng\xE0i tr\u1EEBng ph\u1EA1t h\u1ECD v\xE0 \u0111\u1EC3 cho c\xE1c d\xE2n kh\xE1c ti\xEAu di\u1EC7t h\u1ECD; Ng\xE0i n\xE9m h\u1ECD ra kh\u1ECFi tr\u01B0\u1EDBc m\u1EB7t Ng\xE0i. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v21"
  }, "v21"), mdx("p", null, "Khi CH\xDAA t\xE1ch h\u1ECD ra kh\u1ECFi gia \u0111\xECnh \u0110a-v\xEDt th\xEC d\xE2n \xCDt-ra-en l\u1EADp Gi\xEA-r\xF4-b\xF4-am, con N\xEA-b\xE1t l\xE0m vua. Gi\xEA-r\xF4-b\xF4-am d\u1EABn d\u1EE5 d\xE2n \xCDt-ra-en xa c\xE1ch CH\xDAA v\xE0 d\u1EABn h\u1ECD ph\u1EA1m t\u1ED9i t\xE0y \u0111\xECnh. "), mdx("h6", {
