    "id": "v28"
  }, "v28"), mdx("p", null, "V\u1EADy m\u1ED9t trong c\xE1c th\u1EA7y t\u1EBF l\u1EC5 \u0111\xE3 b\u1ECB \u0111\xE0y t\u1EEB Xa-ma-ri tr\u1EDF v\u1EC1 s\u1ED1ng \u1EDF B\xEA-t\xEAn. \xD4ng d\u1EA1y cho d\xE2n ch\xFAng bi\u1EBFt c\xE1ch th\u1EDD ph\u1EE5ng CH\xDAA. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v29"
  }, "v29"), mdx("p", null, "Nh\u01B0ng m\u1ED7i m\u1ED9t d\xE2n l\u1EADp c\xE1c th\u1EA7n l\u1EA5y cho m\xECnh v\xE0 \u0111\u1EB7t ch\xFAng trong c\xE1c \u0111i\u1EC7n th\u1EDD n\u01A1i th\xE0nh h\u1ECD c\u01B0 ng\u1EE5. Nh\u1EEFng \u0111i\u1EC7n th\u1EDD n\u1EA7y tr\u01B0\u1EDBc kia do ng\u01B0\u1EDDi Xa-ma-ri x\xE2y n\xEAn. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v30"
  }, "v30"), mdx("p", null, "D\xE2n Ba-by-l\xF4n d\u1EF1ng th\u1EA7n Su-c\u1ED1t-B\xEA-n\u1ED1t. D\xE2n Cu-tha th\u1EDD th\u1EA7n N\u1EB9t-ganh. D\xE2n Ha-m\xE1t th\u1EDD th\u1EA7n A-si-ma. "), mdx("h6", {
