  }, "v31"), mdx("p", null, "Ng\u01B0\u1EDDi A-v\xEDt th\u1EDD th\u1EA7n N\xEDp-ha v\xE0 T\u1EA1c-t\u1EAFc. Ng\u01B0\u1EDDi S\xEA-ph\u1EA1t-va-im thi\xEAu con m\xECnh trong l\u1EEDa, d\xE2ng ch\xFAng n\xF3 cho \xC1ch-ra-m\xEA-l\xE9c v\xE0 A-na-m\xEA-l\xE9c, hai th\u1EA7n c\u1EE7a S\xEA-ph\u1EA1t-va-im. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v32"
  }, "v32"), mdx("p", null, "H\u1ECD c\u0169ng t\xF4n th\u1EDD CH\xDAA nh\u01B0ng t\u1EF1 ch\u1ECDn cho m\xECnh c\xE1c th\u1EA7y t\u1EBF l\u1EC5 cho n\u01A1i n\xE0o h\u1ECD th\u1EDD t\xE0 th\u1EA7n. H\u1ECD t\u1EF1 ch\u1ECDn c\xE1c th\u1EA7y t\u1EBF l\u1EC5 trong s\u1ED1 h\u1ECD \u0111\u1EC3 d\xE2ng sinh t\u1EBF cho d\xE2n ch\xFAng. "), mdx("h6", {
